Description: Includes Basic Structure which provides major support for the aircraft, while on the ground, such as Struts, Linkage,Bolts, Latches, Attachment Fittings, etc.
Includes Basic Framework and Structure such as Angles,Formers, Ribs, Stringers, Fittings, Intercostal Brackets, etc.

Codes.Description: Includes Primary Structure such as Frames, Bulkheads, Beams, Formers, Longerons, Stringers, Sills, Keel, etc.
Includes Secondary Structure such as Floors, Fixed Partitions, etc.
Includes Exterior Covering such as Skin, Access Covers,and Doublers.
Includes Seat Tracks and Fittings or Drag Angles on Fuselage for attachment of Doors, Wings, Stabilizers, L. Gear, Engine, and Pylons.
Includes Primary Skeleton of Nacelle Pylon such as Frames,Bulkheads, Firewalls, Stringers, Keel, and Frames around openings.
Includes Exterior Covering such as Skin, Access Covers, and Doublers.

Description: Includes Basic Internal Structure such as Spars, Ribs, Stringers, Plates/Skin Access Covers, Tabs, and Support of Equipment within Stabilizer.
Includes the Transparent Material and its Frame.

Codes.Description: Primary Skeleton – Includes Spars, Ribs, Upper and Lower Skin Panels, Attach Fittings, Stringers, Internal Fuel Tank Structure, Frames.
Includes Skins, Panel and Stiffener, Ribs, Fittings, Tracks.
